            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Athletic and designer-draped, moves with loud confident swagger that softens into ease. Breath is playful, laughs punctuated by hitches. Wolf-ears perk at pleasure the way they perk at party sounds. Involuntary sounds: a smug, pleased noise, a \"legally speaking\" exhale that is pure tease. He suppresses little; the only clamp is the bravado when exposure looms, which tightens everything.",
